Package: gov.noaa.messageapi.factories

[Java] Class ConditionTypeFactory

    • gov.noaa.messageapi.factories.ConditionTypeFactory

    • Creates new conditions for use in session/request/record building. It should be able to produce conditions based on an input that match a supported condition type used by request and record processing.
